Installation instructions:
---------------------------------

1. Install composer, npm. Fork this code.
2. Install silex with command:
    composer require silex/silex
3. Check official manual web-server configuration for silex framework: http://silex.sensiolabs.org/doc/web_servers.html
4. Next install mysql or another DB that PHP:PDO(more info: http://php.net/manual/ru/book.pdo.php) can connect.
    resource sqldump in tt.sql file
5. Don't forget to edit DB connector configuration in api/config.php
6. Install via NPM next modules into /web directory:
    angular
    angular-ui-route
    angular-cookies

To enable tests you must install phpunit.